<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);">
    <!-- Decorative Header Line -->
    <div style="height: 6px; background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #0ea5e9);"></div>
    
    <!-- Email Body Container -->
    <div style="padding: 32px 40px;">
      <!-- Company Branding -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-b: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
        <span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Scrum<span style="color: #4f46e5;">.co.id</span></span>
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 2px;">PT. Adaptiva Sinergi Asia</div>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600;">Yth. Bapak/Ibu <%= @registration.finance_name %>,</p>
      
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Terima kasih atas ketertarikan Anda pada program pelatihan kami. Kami telah menerima permintaan pendaftaran Anda dengan rincian berikut:
      </p>

      <!-- Details Summary Card -->
      <div style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px;">
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; width: 140px; vertical-align: top;">Nama Pelatihan</td>
            <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;"><%= @course.title %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; vertical-align: top;">Jadwal Kelas</td>
            <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px;"><%= @registration.class_schedule.starts_at.strftime('%d %B %Y') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; vertical-align: top;">Jumlah Peserta</td>
            <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px;"><%= @registration.total_participants %> Orang</td>
          </tr>
          <% price = @course.price_for("IDR") || @course.price_for("USD") || @course.course_prices.first %>
          <% if price %>
            <tr>
              <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; vertical-align: top;">Biaya per Peserta</td>
              <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px;"><%= price.display_amount %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;">
              <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-top: 10px; vertical-align: top;">Total Investasi</td>
              <td style="color: #4f46e5; padding-top: 10px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px;">
                <% formatted_total = ActiveSupport::NumberHelper.number_to_delimited(format('%.2f', price.amount.to_f * @registration.total_participants)) %>
                <%= price.currency.upcase %> <%= formatted_total %>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        Kami telah melampirkan dokumen <strong>Penawaran Harga (Quotation)</strong> resmi dalam format PDF pada email ini.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan lebih lanjut mengenai administrasi, jadwal, atau invoice, silakan langsung membalas email ini.
      </p>

      <!-- Signature Block -->
      <div style="border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b;">
        Salam hangat,<br>
        <strong style="color: #0f172a;">Jessica Stella</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Footer Branding -->
    <div style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; text-align: center; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8;">
      Pelatihan Profesional Scrum sejak 2012. Hak Cipta Dilindungi Undang-Undang.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
